OL,3,C'We can't thank them enough': Margaret
OL,4,CLoughlin's SS Vega memories 80 years on
OL,6,FMargaret was born in the early 1930s
OL,7,Fand grew up in St Aubin with her
OL,8,Ffather, mother and elder sister. Most
OL,9,Fof her childhood was spent living
OL,10,Funder German rule.
OL,12,FShe recounts: "We lived at Hillcot in
OL,13,FSt Aubin on the hill. I remember when
OL,14,Fthe Germans arrived they were all in
OL,15,Forder and walking up the hill.
OL,17,F"Of course, we went outside and stood
OL,18,Fon the doorstep to look at the Germans
OL,19,Farriving - it was frightening
OL,20,Factually."
