OL,3,C'We can't thank them enough': Margaret
OL,4,CLoughlin's SS Vega memories 80 years on
OL,6,FMargaret remembers that moment as if
OL,7,Fit were yesterday, along with other
OL,8,Fmemories that no child should have to
OL,9,Frecall.
OL,11,FShe recalls: "One morning we went
OL,12,Foutside and there were our six
OL,13,Frabbits' heads all on the doorstep.
OL,14,FThey'd been stolen during the night
OL,15,Fand they just left the heads - that
OL,16,Fwas horrendous.
OL,18,F"It's things that don't go away."
