OL,3,C'We can't thank them enough': Margaret
OL,4,CLoughlin's SS Vega memories 80 years on
OL,6,FAfter years of conforming to the Nazi
OL,7,Fregime, Margaret eventually decided to
OL,8,Frebel.
OL,10,F"I stole a block of coal because we
OL,11,Fhad no coal - nothing.
OL,13,F"My mother and father had a fit when I
OL,14,Fgot back home because it was just down
OL,15,Fthe road but I was determined to do it
OL,16,Fbecause I knew that they were
OL,17,Fsuffering.
OL,19,F"It's just one of those things you do
OL,20,Fon the spur of the moment (when) you
OL,21,Fknow you're desperate."
