OL,3,C'We can't thank them enough': Margaret
OL,4,CLoughlin's SS Vega memories 80 years on
OL,6,FAt the time, Margaret was 13 and
OL,7,Frecalls the Red Cross parcels' arrival
OL,8,Fbeing "like Christmas".
OL,10,FShe adds: "I can remember walking up
OL,11,Fthe hill after getting it and holding
OL,12,Fmy Red Cross parcel.
OL,14,F"It was fantastic (...) I couldn't
OL,15,Fwait to get home to open it up and
OL,16,Ffind out what's inside."
OL,18,FWhat did the Red Cross parcels contain?
OL,20,FThe Canadian parcels contained:
