OL,3,C'We can't thank them enough': Margaret
OL,4,CLoughlin's SS Vega memories 80 years on
OL,6,FShe concludes: "We can't forget that
OL,7,Fyear and we can't thank them enough.
OL,8,FYou know you can't repay people for
OL,9,Fthings like that - you'd like to.
OL,11,F"Please god, never happen again."
